---
title: Quick Honey-Soy Chicken & Garlicky Greens with Radish Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: Flavoursome and simply delicious, this stir-fry brings together quick-cooking diced chicken with a colourful radish slaw. The sneaky addition of crispy shallots for garnish is the best way to round out this delicious low-carb meal!

